dc_title_s: District and Commune Boundaries, Republic of the Congo, 2007
dc_description_s: This line shapefile contains district and commune boundaries for the Republic of the Congo as of January 2007. This layer is part of the Map Library dataset containing line and polygon boundaries for individual countries on the African continent.The Map Library is a project of the UK charity â€œThe Map Maker Trust." It aims to make public domain mapping data more readily available for development in all kinds of fields, from health care to urban management, from de-mining to environmental protection.
